      <h1>Motivation</h1>
      <br>
      <br>
      <p class="black"> At the time of this project, San Jose State University does not have a dedicated professional
        social media service that assists students
        in making connections with companies. With that in mind, the motivation is to create a web application that is
        able to fulfill that role.
        The creators of ProConnect wanted to make an application that recruiters for companies can default to when
        scouting for applicants. In
        addition, ProConnect also allows users to search for companies that they may be interested in. Students attend
        school in order to acquire
        knowledge for the industry they want to see themselves in. ProConnect is important in that it forms a bridge
        from school to real world
        industries. The problem of students not being able to network with companies through San Jose State University
        is now solved through
        ProConnect’s social platform.
      </p>

